{"tid":894010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大獲！Nancy Pelosi在六四發生時曾在天安門廣場外靜坐抗議，及反對中國申辦奧運","createTime":"2018-11-08T05:26:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T09:03:21.000Z","uid":60281,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a21a8170f648d8159acf65e5addf2cfb6f0265c1","tid":894010,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T05:26:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://frankwarner.typepad.com/.a/6a00d83451cd3769e2011570c825c5970b-600wi\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffrankwarner.typepad.com%2F.a%2F6a00d83451cd3769e2011570c825c5970b-600wi&h=3c303289&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蘭希&middot;佩洛西擔任眾議員以來，一直關注中國人權見稱，十多年來一直投票反對給中國最惠國待遇、中國申辦奧運會等，在2007年6月12日即以眾議院議長身分發表聲明要求美國介入調查中國廠商的剝削童工。<br />\n<br />\n六四事件發生時，她曾在天安門廣場外靜坐抗議，旨在為六四事件時期的中國學生提供庇護的中國學生保護法案即是由她提出。<br />\n<br />\n1992年，佩洛西獲中國民主教育基金會頒發第7屆傑出民主人士獎。<br />\n<br />\n佩洛西與前任參議院民主黨少數黨領袖哈里&middot;瑞德同屬民主黨內的對華強硬派，主張與中國進行人權對話，並經常批評中國的人權狀況。"},{"pid":"58c19cf267dea364396a29761b5ee79bca842e2a","tid":894010,"uid":1441,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T05:27:47.000Z","msg":"咁關心贏國，贏國又贏!"},{"pid":"1e2267db2f444a002aa9f2fc843cbbaf3db2d646","tid":894010,"uid":3167,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T05:28:23.000Z","msg":"中國心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 美國玩撚完"},{"pid":"f8f5e03498bbd468173215adeac1ba7153043cd2","tid":894010,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T05:29:16.000Z","msg":"建設民主中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fea8033754e4082b5306e174024422ef111df163","tid":894010,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T05:30:26.000Z","msg":"講人權, 支那邊會覺得痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0667033f8dae29295a7700eab43ff081fa23e265","tid":8